        <abstract> 
<p>Spent two days watching <hi rend="italic">Epipactis palustris</hi> in a bog. Never saw a moth.</p> 
            <p>Thinks "Suddenism" and not "Graduality" is the great Law of Nature.</p>
        </abstract>
